---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Industry-Specific Quantum Solutions"
  description="Tailored quantum computing solutions for diverse industry sectors"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Quantum Solutions by Industry</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Financial Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>• Portfolio optimization</li>
          <li>• Risk assessment</li>
          <li>• Fraud detection</li>
          <li>• Trading strategies</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Achieve superior returns and risk management through quantum algorithms</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Healthcare & Pharma</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>• Drug discovery</li>
          <li>• Protein folding</li>
          <li>• Clinical trials optimization</li>
          <li>• Patient data analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Accelerate research and improve patient outcomes with quantum computing</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Manufacturing</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>• Supply chain optimization</li>
          <li>• Quality control</li>
          <li>• Process simulation</li>
          <li>• Resource allocation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Optimize operations and reduce costs with quantum-powered solutions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Core Technologies</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Optimization Algorithms</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Quantum Annealing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Optimal solution finding for complex problems</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">QAOA</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Combinatorial optimization for business problems</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Machine Learning</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">QML Models</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Enhanced pattern recognition and classification</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Quantum Neural Networks</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Advanced deep learning capabilities</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Implementation Process</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      {[
        {
          step: "1",
          title: "Assessment",
          description: "Industry-specific requirements analysis"
        },
        {
          step: "2",
          title: "Solution Design",
          description: "Custom quantum algorithm development"
        },
        {
          step: "3",
          title: "Integration",
          description: "Seamless system implementation"
        },
        {
          step: "4",
          title: "Optimization",
          description: "Continuous performance improvement"
        }
      ].map((phase) => (
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            {phase.step}
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">{phase.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{phase.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Transform Your Industry</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Ready to leverage quantum computing for your specific industry needs? Let's discuss how our solutions can drive innovation and efficiency in your organization.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
        Schedule a Consultation
      </a>
      <a href="/services/quantum/workforce" class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
        Explore Workforce Development
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>